<P>THAT Major <HI>Joshua Thomas, William Watson</HI> and <HI>Isaac Lothrop,</HI> Esq'rs. be, and they hereby are appointed a Committee, to wait on the Rev. <HI>Samuel West,</HI> with the Thanks of this Town, for his learned and ingenious Sermon, delivered in this Town, on the last An|niversary of the landing of our Fathers here, and request a Copy thereof, that it may be printed.</P>
